snippet.title: Me & My Katamari - Opening Intro (Upscaled to FullHD1080p)
snippet.description:
Opening Intro from "Me & My Katamari" for "Sony PlayStation Portable" system with resolution upscale improvements. Video was captured from USA-region version of game (ULUS10094)

Upscaled original 480x272 to 1920x1088(x4) with Video2X using Waifu2X NCNN (Vulkan) driver.
Video2X on GitHub: https://github.com/k4yt3x/video2x

Original unedited USA (ULUS10094) version: https://youtu.be/i_lwxxx2P00
Unedited Japanese (ULJS00033) version: https://youtu.be/5Go7ILYRpTY
